    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, appearing and driving just as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine, and the interior is immaculate, showing absolutely no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a silent engine, crisp shifting, and every feature functioning exactly as intended. This is a rare opportunity to own a meticulously preserved example that has been stored in a climate-controlled environment and maintained to the highest possible standards.",
